'''巴西帕爾馬斯FR球隊班機空難'''是一次發生於2021年1月24日的空難。

==飛機==
本次發生空難的飛機是[[比奇飛機公司|比奇飛機公司]]的“比奇男爵”，註冊號為PT-LYG

==事故過程==
事故發生在2021年1月24日上午8時15分左右。<ref name="newsbook1">{{Cite web|title=Plane crash kills Palmas FR club president and 4 players|url=https://newsbook.com.mt/en/plane-crash-kills-palmas-fr-club-president-and-4-players/|accessdate=2021-03-07|date=2021-01-24|last=Farrugia|first=Cedric|work=Newsbook|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-01-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210124173021/https://newsbook.com.mt/en/plane-crash-kills-palmas-fr-club-president-and-4-players/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

目擊者的報告表明，與地面的碰撞是在嘗試起飛後數秒，隨後發生爆炸。<ref name="globo1">{{Cite web|title=Piloto do avião que caiu com jogadores do Palmas tinha mais de 30 anos de experiência, diz amigo|url=https://g1.globo.com/to/tocantins/noticia/2021/01/25/piloto-do-aviao-que-caiu-com-jogadores-do-palmas-tinha-mais-de-30-anos-de-experiencia-diz-amigo.ghtml|accessdate=2021-03-07|work=G1|language=pt-br|archive-date=2021-01-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210125222657/https://g1.globo.com/to/tocantins/noticia/2021/01/25/piloto-do-aviao-que-caiu-com-jogadores-do-palmas-tinha-mais-de-30-anos-de-experiencia-diz-amigo.ghtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==遇難者==
巴西{{le|足球俱樂部帕爾馬斯|Palmas Futebol e Regatas}}球隊總裁盧卡斯·梅拉（Lucas Meira）以及球員盧卡斯·普拉克西德斯（Lucas Praxedes），{{le|吉列爾梅·諾爾|Guilherme Noé}}（{{lang-pt|Guilherme Noé}}），{{le|拉努爾|Ranule}}（{{lang-pt|Ranule}}）和{{le|馬庫斯·莫利納里|Marcus Molinari}}（{{lang-pt|Marcus Molinari}}），以及機長瓦格納·馬查度·祖利亞（{{lang-pt|Wagner Machado Júnior}}）均在飛機墜毀後喪生。<ref name="foxsport1">{{Cite web|title=Football players, club president dead after Brazilian plane crash|url=https://www.foxsports.com.au/football/football-news-2021-palmas-football-club-plane-crash-lucas-meira-lucas-praxedes-guilherme-noe-ranule-marcus-molinari/news-story/79cd10be878b70e06fc1e98f61822b8a|accessdate=2021-03-07|date=2021-01-24|work=Fox Sports|language=en|archive-date=2021-01-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210124200501/https://www.foxsports.com.au/football/football-news-2021-palmas-football-club-plane-crash-lucas-meira-lucas-praxedes-guilherme-noe-ranule-marcus-molinari/news-story/79cd10be878b70e06fc1e98f61822b8a|dead-url=no}}</ref>

